		<div class="telo" style="margin-top:5%; margin-bottom:0%">
			<p align = "left" class="text" style="margin-top:2.5%; margin-bottom:0%"> The first ever international match was played in 1872 - England vs Scotland.
				The official birthday of the soccer rules is December 7, 1863 (they were introduced by the English
				Soccer Association). Although the first attempts to legalize the sport were already in 1846, 
				at a meeting of English colleges. Then this attempt was not successful.
				New rules were established by FIFA (the year of foundation of the organization - 1904) together with IFAB 
				(International Football Association Board: England, Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland).
				Their latest revision took place in 2019 - 2020. <br><br></p>
		</div>
		<div class="telo" >
			<img src = "static/images/sheffild.png" alt = "«Sheffield»" class="photo" style="margin-top:2%;">
			<p class="text" style="margin-top:6%">
				The first professional football club founded in 1857 was Sheffield FC. <br><br>
				Football was brought to the British Isles by the Italians back in the XIV century, the game was called "Calcio". 
				So it's more accurate to call the English the originators of professional football,
				because the ball game was invented long before them. <br><br> 
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="telo" style="display: block; padding-top: 1px;">
			<p class="text"> <b>Key changes in football: </b> </p>
			<ul class="formli" style="margin-right: 1%;" >
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1863 year - </b> The first official rules are created <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1869 year - </b> Goal kicks have been introduced <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1872 year - </b> The emergence of angles <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1875 year - </b> Crossbars have been added to the goalposts <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1878 year - </b> The referee blew his whistle <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1886 year - </b> Establishment of the Council of the International Football Association (IFAB) <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1891 year - </b> For the first time, an eleven-metre kick (penalty kick)<br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1902 year - </b> This year, the penalty kick has become a penalty kick from a specific spot, 
					rather than anywhere along the 11-metre line. <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1904 year - </b> FIFA was created in Paris <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1912 year - </b> Goalkeepers were only allowed to play with their hands in the penalty area, not all over the pitch <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1913 year - </b> FIFA and IFAB have merged <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1920 year - </b> The offside rule has been changed. From now on, offside after a throw-in.
					from outside the box is no longer recorded <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1925 year - </b> The offside rule has changed from three players between the player and the goal to two players <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1937 year - </b> Finalised the penalty area (added a half-circle at the top) <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1938 year - </b> Stanley Rowse led the group in changing the rules <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1990 year - </b> As of this year, offside is not recorded if a player is in line
					with the penultimate player <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1992 year - </b> Goalkeepers have been banned from picking up the ball after a deliberate pass from their own goalkeepers <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>1998 year - </b> A hard tackle from behind was penalised with a red card <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>2009 year - </b> The referees have appeared outside the gates <br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>2013 year - </b> Started goal detection technology (whether the ball has crossed the goal line)<br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>2017 year - </b> VAR (video assistant referee) tested for the first time<br></li>
				<li style="margin-bottom: 1%;"><b>2021 year - </b> UEFA abolished the away goal rule (introduced in 1965). <br><br></li>
			</ul>
